{"product_id":"madara-balancing-toner-200ml","title":"MÁDARA Balancing Toner 200ml","description":"\u003cp\u003eReturn skin back to its healthy state with this refreshing and regulating toner. The pH balancing formula with conditioning extracts of raspberries and cucumber, floral waters and skin-identical natural moisturisers minimises pores and deeply tones and conditions the skin, leaving it clean, fresh and vibrant.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cdiv\u003eHelps to renew skin’s protective layer and regulate its natural pH balance.\u003c\/div\u003e\n\u003cdiv\u003ePackaged in a 100% post-consumer recycled bottle.\u003c\/div\u003e\n\u003cdiv\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\u003c\/div\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan style=\"font-size: 0.875rem;\"\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eHow to use: \u003c\/strong\u003eApply in the morning and night to clean skin with a cotton pad or splash on with hands. Follow with moisturiser.\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eIngredients:\u003c\/strong\u003e AQUA; GLYCERIN**; ROSA DAMASCENA (ROSE) FLOWER WATER*; CUCUMIS SATIVUS (CUCUMBER) FRUIT EXTRACT*; RUBUS IDAEUS (RASPBERRY) FRUIT EXTRACT*; SODIUM PCA; BETAINE; PROPANEDIOL; HAMAMELIS VIRGINIANA (WITCH HAZEL) LEAF WATER*; SODIUM LEVULINATE; PHENETHYL ALCOHOL; SODIUM BENZOATE; CHAMOMILLA RECUTITA (CAMOMILE) FLOWER EXTRACT*; PLANTAGO MAJOR (PLANTAIN) LEAF EXTRACT*; CITRIC ACID; BENZYL ALCOHOL; RHAMNOSE; XYLITYLGLUCOSIDE; POTASSIUM SORBATE; ANHYDROXYLITOL; GLUCOSE; GLUCURONIC ACID; XYLITOL\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e*Ingredients from Organic Farming **Made using organic ingredients\u003cbr\u003e\u003cbr\u003e99% Natural origin of total\u003cbr\u003e10% Organic of total\u003cbr\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e* Please note that ingredient lists may change and slightly vary from time to time. You will always find the most up-to-date information on the actual product packaging.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003c!----\u003e","brand":"MADARA","offers":[{"title":"Default Title","offer_id":53351940948295,"sku":null,"price":17.9,"currency_code":"EUR","in_stock":true}],"thumbnail_url":"\/\/cdn.shopify.com\/s\/files\/1\/0790\/6829\/9591\/files\/madara-balancing-toner-200ml-7756224.jpg?v=1771463662","url":"https:\/\/bioskina.com\/products\/madara-balancing-toner-200ml","provider":"bioskina","version":"1.0","type":"link"}